divs: Sighting DetailsI recently noticed the object in a photo I shot of my wife while attending the Doheny Blues Festival in 2006. The object in the photo shows a bright yellow color which looks like it could be from exhaust; the direction is wrong for it to be a reflection from the sun or a sundog. I did not see the object when shooting the photo or with the naked eye. I do not recall any sound either.
